description: The Belkin F5X003 Home Antenna for XM improves your XM satellite radio receivers indoor reception. Featuring a built-in deskstand, a wall-mount option, and a 20-foot cable, this antenna is built for versatile positioning in your home or office. The F5X003 is compatible with the Xpress, RoadyXT, MyFi, TAO XM2go, and AirWare, and it includes a Belkin one-year warranty.
